<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFSinger1976">Singer, Harold L. (March 28, 1976). "An Open Letter to Ed Roberts". <i>Micro-8 Computer User Group Newsletter</i> (Lompoc, CA: Cabrillo Computer Center) <b>2</b> (4): p. 1.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=An+Open+Letter+to+Ed+Roberts&amp;rft.jtitle=Micro-8+Computer+User+Group+Newsletter&amp;rft.aulast=Singer&amp;rft.aufirst=Harold+L.&amp;rft.au=Singer%2C+Harold+L.&amp;rft.date=March+28%2C+1976&amp;rft.volume=2&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=p.+1&amp;rft.place=Lompoc%2C+CA&amp;rft.pub=Cabrillo+Computer+Center&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Open_Letter_to_Hobbyists"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ul>
